g.title: ArthurRank1Convo3 begins.
g.text: ArthurRank1Convo3 begins.

g.title: j4292596478
g.text: I'd love to take your Atomicycle for a ride.

g.title: j1472196057
g.text: Hey mind if I borrow your Atomicycle? ;)

g.title: j3813711070
g.text: No.

g.title: j430597857
g.text: If you touch it I'll murder you in your Sol-loving sleep.

g.title: j2933958659
g.text: C'mon. What's the worst that could happen?

g.title: j3519864902
g.text: Okay, you drive. I'll sit on the back. Joyride.

g.title: j2734241758
g.text: And no one will find the corpse.

g.title: j328132703
g.text: *No.*

g.title: j958408651
g.text: Trust me.

g.title: j1329883069
g.text: Why not?

g.title: j1532448586
g.text: Fine. [End.]

g.title: j1682069442
g.text: Chill! I was just playing around!

g.title: j1175107569
g.text: Forget I said anything. [End.]

g.title: j3955004985
g.text: Because that thing is my pride and joy. And you'll take it and ruin it.

g.title: Chat ends.
g.text: Chat ends.

g.title: j354783735
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j2747401661
g.text: Why would you assume I'd take something of yours and - oh...

g.title: j19578339
g.text: Fine. I'll go get my own. And it'll be cooler anyway. [End.]

g.title: j3924026480
g.text: How was I supposed to know?!

g.title: j3988593880
g.text: Point taken.

g.title: j3761449733
g.text: I'll just... use my own instead...

g.title: j531779007
g.text: I'm sure it will be.

g.title: j1518729425
g.text: That's what the winky face was for!

g.title: j207691483
g.text: Never mind. [End.]

g.title: j2928755249
g.text: You might be a lot of things, Drifter. But at least you're not stupid.

g.title: j2084410780
g.text: Sigh.

g.title: j49250918
g.text: What "winky face?"

g.title: j2496918664
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j1931647555
g.text: Tilt your head to the left and look for the face. That's called an "emoticon."

g.title: j224973429
g.text: You're starting to make a lot more sense, now...

g.title: j2003093707
g.text: I came off harsh. Tell you what. When you get your own? We'll go riding together.

g.title: j4142980767
g.text: Emotion + Icon. Emoticon.

g.title: j2629841812
g.text: Oh.

g.title: j602729539
g.text: They sound a lot better than those messed-up horses you mentioned.

g.title: j2597453578
g.text: +10 Chemistry

g.title: j3979154778
g.text: Well...shit. I think I need to apologize to Aoi for...a lot. Be right back.

g.title: j2059869675
g.text: Boolean ArthurAoiEmoticon is now true.
